Class MapData

    • com.mapzen.tangram.MapData

  • public class MapData

    • Method Detail

      • setFeatures

        public void setFeatures(java.util.List<Geometry> features)
        Assign a list of features to this data collection. This replaces any previously assigned feature lists or GeoJSON data.
        Parameters:
        features - The features to assign

      • setGeoJson

        public void setGeoJson(java.lang.String data)
        Assign features described in a GeoJSON string to this collection. This will replace any previously assigned feature lists or GeoJSON data.
        Parameters:
        data - A string containing a GeoJSON FeatureCollection

      • name

        public java.lang.String name()
        Get the name of this MapData.
        Returns:
        The name.

      • remove

        public void remove()
        Remove this MapData from the map it is currently associated with. Using this object after remove is called will cause an exception to be thrown. remove is called on every MapData associated with a map when its MapController is destroyed.

      • clear

        public void clear()
        Remove all features from this collection.
